			<p>
				<p style="margin-bottom:11px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif">SECI has been catering to domestic clients and is now looking to expand its scope to international clients as well. Due to global commitments, the country is moving toward faster adoption of Renewable Energy, as a result of which an increased number of PSUs/government agencies are foraying into this sector. SECI provides its expertise to such clients in bringing up RE projects and aims at executing a larger share of consultancy projects in the coming years.</span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-bottom:11px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif"><span lang="EN-GB" style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif">Major ongoing/planned Projects are as mentioned below:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

